# Robotics Final Project

Autonomous obstacle avoidance robot using Arduino Uno and ESP32 IoT communication.

## Project Architecture

### Arduino Uno
Handles:
- motor control
- ultrasonic sensor
- servo scanning
- obstacle avoidance logic

### ESP32
Handles:
- WiFi connection
- MQTT communication
- IoT monitoring/dashboard

### Communication
Arduino Uno and ESP32 communicate using UART serial communication.

Example message:
```text
DIST=18,MODE=AUTO,TURN=LEFT